00:30:00,299 --> 00:30:02,067
Of course.

541
00:30:02,601 --> 00:30:04,236
That's great!

542
00:30:04,303 --> 00:30:05,337
Shancai.

543
00:30:08,707 --> 00:30:10,108
<i>You have to be careful, though,</i>

544
00:30:10,175 --> 00:30:11,510
