643
00:35:41,539 --> 00:35:43,708
-How could this happen?
-I didn't expect she will do this.

644
00:35:45,310 --> 00:35:46,478
Shancai.

645
00:35:46,544 --> 00:35:47,746
Li Zhen.

646
00:35:47,812 --> 00:35:49,280
