659
00:36:14,406 --> 00:36:15,707
Don't wait for him to give her one.

660
00:36:15,774 --> 00:36:17,175
Let's start tomorrow.

661
00:36:17,242 --> 00:36:18,376
Isn't this fun?

662
00:36:18,443 --> 00:36:20,145
We can play games again.

663
00:36:23,581 --> 00:36:29,521
<i>Good times don't last long</i>

664
00:36:29,587 --> 00:36:36,027
<i>Every day is not a Sunday</i>

665
00:36:36,094 --> 00:36:39,764
