716
00:39:24,529 --> 00:39:25,363
Daoming Si.

717
00:39:25,430 --> 00:39:26,798
I don't care what other people think.

718
00:39:26,865 --> 00:39:28,199
I just want you to believe me.

719
00:39:28,266 --> 00:39:29,400
That's just a misunderstanding.

720
00:39:29,467 --> 00:39:30,768
I don't care what others think of me.

721
00:39:30,835 --> 00:39:32,303
